title: Fallen Timbers Battlefield and Fort Miamis National Historic Site: Things To Know Before You Come
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Things To Know Before You Come             Things To Know Before You Come       Passport Stamps Until the Battlefield is open, visitors can have their National Parks Passport stamped at the Maumee Branch of the Toledo-Lucas County Public Library, located on River Road.
